    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0815a07"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>京兆大安國寺<persName key="A011214">利涉</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0815a08"/><persName key="A011214">釋利涉</persName>者，本<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>人也，即大梵婆羅門<ptr type="glossary" target="#g117"/>之種<lb
ed="T" n="0815a09"/>姓。夙齡<anchor xml:id="beg0815002"/>疆<anchor xml:id="end0815002"/>志，機警溢倫，宗黨之中，推其達<lb
ed="T" n="0815a10"/>法。欲遊<placeName key="PL000000000083">震旦</placeName>，結侶東征，至金梭嶺<!--找不到此地-->，遇<persName key="A000294">玄<lb
ed="T" n="0815a11"/>奘三藏</persName>，行次相逢，禮求<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>度。既而群經眾論，<lb
ed="T" n="0815a12"/>鑿竅通幽，特爾遠塵，歸乎正道，非<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>難其<lb
ed="T" n="0815a13"/>移轉矣。<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>門賢哲輻湊，<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>季孟於<persName key="A000060">光</persName>、<persName key="A000746">寶</persName>之間。<lb
ed="T" n="0815a14"/>其為人也，猶帛高座之放曠。<persName key="A002100">中宗</persName>最加欽重，<lb
ed="T" n="0815a15"/>朝廷卿相感義與遊。<date from-iso="0713" key="j19818371992113" to-iso="0742">開元</date>中於<placeName key="PL000000042180">安國寺</placeName>講<lb
ed="T" n="0815a16"/>《華嚴經》，四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>赴堂，遲則無容膝之位矣。檀<lb
ed="T" n="0815a17"/>施繁熾，利動人心。有<placeName key="PL000000023277">頴陽</placeName>人<persName key="A011830">韋玎</persName>，<date from-iso="0685" key="j19712941972741" to-iso="0689">垂拱</date>中中<lb
ed="T" n="0815a18"/>第，調選<placeName key="PL000000005199">河中府</placeName>文學，遷大理評事祕校。見<lb
ed="T" n="0815a19"/><persName key="A011214">涉</persName>講筵幣帛堆積，就乞選糧，所獲未厭。表<lb
ed="T" n="0815a20"/>請釋道二教定其勝負，言釋道蠧政可除。<lb
ed="T" n="0815a21"/><persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>詔三教各選一百人，都集內殿，<persName key="A011830">韋玎</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0815a22"/>先陟高座，挫<persName key="A011831">葉靜能</persName>及空門<persName key="A011832">思明</persName>，例皆辭<lb
ed="T" n="0815a23"/>屈。<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>次登座，解疑釋結，臨敵有餘，與<persName key="A011830">韋</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0815a24"/>往返百數千言，條緒交亂，相次抗之，棼絲自<lb
ed="T" n="0815a25"/>理，正直有歸。<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>重問<persName key="A011830">韋</persName>曰：「子先登席，可非<lb
ed="T" n="0815a26"/>主耶？未審主人何姓？」<persName key="A011830">玎</persName>曰：「姓韋。」<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>將韋字<lb
ed="T" n="0815a27"/>為韻，揭調長吟。偈詞曰：「我之佛法是無為，<lb
ed="T" n="0815a28"/>何故今朝得有為？無<persName key="A012119">韋</persName>始得三數載，不知此<lb
ed="T" n="0815a29"/>復是何韋？」<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>之吟作，百官悚然。<ref type="person" target="#A000291">帝</ref>果憶<persName key="A012119"><anchor xml:id="beg0815003"/>何<anchor xml:id="end0815003"/><pb ed="T" n="0815b" xml:id="T50.2061.0815b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0815b01"/>韋</persName>之事，凜然變色曰：「<persName key="A011830">玎</persName>是<ref type="person" target="#A012119">庶人</ref>宗族，敢爾輕<lb
ed="T" n="0815b02"/>懱<ref type="person" target="#A000291">朕</ref>玄元祖教及凌𨏦釋門。」<persName key="A011830">玎</persName>下殿俯伏待<lb
ed="T" n="0815b03"/>罪，叩頭言：「<ref type="person" target="#A011830">臣</ref>非<ref type="person" target="#A012119">庶人</ref>之屬。」<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>貴其鉗利<lb
ed="T" n="0815b04"/>口以解疎狂，奏曰：「<persName key="A011830">玎</persName>是<placeName key="PL000000042002">關</placeName>外之人，非<persName key="A019417">玄貞</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0815b05"/>之族類。」勅貶<placeName key="PL000000033568">象州</placeName>，百姓賜<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>錢絹，助造明<lb
ed="T" n="0815b06"/>教寺<!--找不到此地-->，加號<persName key="A011214">明教</persName>焉。二教重熙，<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>之力也。因<lb
ed="T" n="0815b07"/>著《立法幢論》一卷。公卿間有言曰：「<persName key="A011214">涉公</persName>是<persName key="A011830">韋<lb
ed="T" n="0815b08"/>掾</persName>之膏盲也。」<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>曰：「此舉也，矢在弦上，不得<lb
ed="T" n="0815b09"/>不發。」自此<placeName key="PL000000042189">京城</placeName>無不改觀，言談講者，以<lb
ed="T" n="0815b10"/><persName key="A011214">涉</persName>為最焉。晚節遭其譴謫<placeName key="PL000000028309">漢東</placeName>，尋屬寬宥，<lb
ed="T" n="0815b11"/>移徙南陽<placeName key="PL000000025196">龍興寺</placeName>。時<persName key="A001707">惠忠國師</persName>知重<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>名，聊<lb
ed="T" n="0815b12"/>欵關相謁，曰：「納衣小僧向前，<ref type="person" target="#A011214">某</ref>被門徒朝要<lb
ed="T" n="0815b13"/>連坐于此，適觀<ref type="person" target="#A001707">師</ref>當有貴氣，可作高道國<lb
ed="T" n="0815b14"/>德，勿同<ref type="person" target="#A011214">吾</ref>也。」乃開篋提衣物，令<persName key="A001707">忠師</persName>曳<lb
ed="T" n="0815b15"/>婁，由此<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000025497">鄧</placeName>之人皆驚<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>如此懸記，<persName key="A001707">忠師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0815b16"/>道聲又光闡焉，蓋<persName key="A011214">涉</persName>望重之故也。<date from-iso="0761-02-14" key="j19990541999309" to-iso="0761-10-27">上元二年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0815b17"/>詔<persName key="A001707">忠師</persName>入供養。<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>時入宮起居<persName key="A000291">太上皇</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0815b18"/>乃引<persName key="A001707">忠</persName>見<persName key="A000291">上皇</persName>曰：「此人何如<persName key="A011214">利涉</persName>？」則知<persName key="A011214">涉</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0815b19"/>才業優長，帝王器重，復多著述。<date from-iso="0766" key="j20011912005747" to-iso="0779">大曆</date>中<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明<lb
ed="T" n="0815b20"/>寺</placeName>翻經沙門<persName key="A001417">圓照</persName>撰《涉傳》，成一十卷，足知<lb
ed="T" n="0815b21"/>言行之多也矣。</p>
